trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> elements.
trans-unit.target: 表示 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> 項目的集合。

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" /> defines the allowable child content of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Section" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.ListItem" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TableCell" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Floater" />, and <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Figure" /> elements.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" /> 會定義 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument" />、<see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Section" />、<see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.ListItem" />、<see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.TableCell" />、<see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Floater" /> 及 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Figure" /> 項目的可允許子內容。

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection> creation is only permitted inside an element that owns a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection>, such as a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument> or <xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection> 建立只允許擁有項目內<xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection>，例如<xref:System.Windows.Documents.FlowDocument>或<xref:System.Windows.Documents.TextElement>。

trans-unit.source: As such, a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection> cannot be instantiated directly and has no default or overloaded constructor.
trans-unit.target: 因此，<xref:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection>無法直接執行個體化，沒有預設值或多載建構函式。

trans-unit.source: Gets the first <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> element within this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 取得這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> 執行個體內的第一個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" /> 項目。

trans-unit.source: The first <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> element in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> 中的第一個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" /> 項目。

trans-unit.source: Gets the last <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> element within this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: 取得這個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> 執行個體內的最後一個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" /> 項目。

trans-unit.source: The last <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> element in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Block" /> 中的最後一個 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.BlockCollection" /> 項目。
